This paper deals with data protection and leakage, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also proposes a solution that involves data allocation and transfer, which could be related to data structures (cs.DS) and databases (cs.DB). The paper also mentions the use of a ledger to log data sharing operations, which could be related to machine learning (cs.LG) and software engineering (cs.SE).
